          "Layer_Thickness_um": 30.0,
          "Hatch_Spacing_um": 100.0,
          "Protective_Atmosphere": "Argon"
        }
      },
      "Microstructure_Info": {
        "Microstructure_Text": {
          "original": "The as-fabricated sample showed a coarse columnar grain microstructure, heterogeneous element distribution, high density of dislocations, and complex precipitation types. There are three different forms of the precipitates: white precipitates rich in Cu and Mg, grey precipitates rich in O (Al2O3), and black precipitates containing Li (δ' Al3Li). [cite: 516, 517, 519, 532]",
          "simplified": "Coarse columnar grains with heterogeneous elemental distribution and high dislocation density. Complex precipitates include Cu/Mg-rich phases, Al2O3, and δ' (Al3Li). [cite: 20, 516, 517, 519, 532]"
        },
